Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:18.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:30.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:36.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:41.97,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:48.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:58.06,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:06.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:12.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:24.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:46.60,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zentradi factory satellite captured\Nas a result of the space expedition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:50.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,has been placed in orbit near the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:55.52,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,137)}SATAN'S DOLLS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect themselves from external\Nthreats such as the Zentradi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:17.68,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and their enemies, the Supervision Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.82,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the New Earth UN Government has\Nbegun mass weapons production.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.25,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, much of the factory's\Nmachinery was destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.79,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,by repeated Supervision Army attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and even components that remained operational\Nsoon began to break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:11.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This started happening almost as soon\Nas it got here. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There is some unfortunate news I must deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I suppose I have to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The future's not looking too bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:36.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,About Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:39.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They say things aren't going\Nwell between her and Kaifun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from those cleaners,\NLoli and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Loli and them said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he said they saw them arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't it have been just one time\Nthey happened to be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were saying some\Npretty nasty things to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What do you think the problem is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When an entertainer hits hard times,\Nthey start trouble like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard times?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that to happen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Minmay's found\Nherself another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avoid idle talk\Nwhile we're on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:32.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, ma'am! There's been\Na disturbance in Trad City.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them to send a patrol unit there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:47.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:52.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Machizaki? Tell Captain Vanessa\Nto return to Command Section 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:58.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, ma'am, but could you\Npossibly tell her that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'd really rather not talk to those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:04.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They always start picking on me!\NPlease, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear. Men these days are all wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Trad City! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:24.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But Trad City is over half Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we handle this with just three units?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Other units should be coming too,\Nso stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody's gotta argue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole the micloning device!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Scramble the Valkyries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are. Stop them\Nwith some warning shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:15.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to live your lives\Nhowever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:54.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't go running off\Nwith that micloning device!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You haven't secured it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:14.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, with patrols this tight, things\Nhaven't really gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb bastard! Just crush their\Npatrols with your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Oigur! You've grown\Nweak-willed these past two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:32.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should be able to smash your way in\Nand steal a micloning device or two, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:36.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit tryin' to make it sound so easy!\NWith our current firepower...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.52,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you use that tone to\Naddress a superior officer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! This isn't the time for you two\Nto be standing around arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur! I already said I'd turn\Neveryone back to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:50.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so if I don't get that micloning device,\NI'll look like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever it takes.\NJust go and steal one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can that man really be counted on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:06.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to how he used to be, he's\Na complete wimp, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one that's as powerful as ever is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to have them handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:19.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go steal that\Nmicloning device myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So easy to manipulate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're taking this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The military is taking custody of this device.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to make things difficult for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, most of our\Npopulation is Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be extremely inconvenient\Nnot to have the device on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the military understood that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We do, but circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:29.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you understand what\Na dangerous time this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some Zentradi who can't\Nget used to life on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,who are dissatisfied and have\Nstarted turning violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:47.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would happen if those dissatisfied elements joined forces and made themselves giants to become more powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect the micloning\Ndevice from rioters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The military will take custody of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, you're twisting the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:07.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zentradi have the right to become giants\Nor miclones whenever they choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:08.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:12.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't it a bit cruel to remove\Na micloning device
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,from a city where a great deal\Nof Zentradi live?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The military ain't gonna get its way this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The military taking custody of this is\Nan unjust use of political power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is within its rights\Nto keep this device!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That youngster's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell you tryin' to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This city has almost no firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if the rioters\Ncome here to steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, the residents\Nwill protect it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if we protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the military do whatever\Nthe hell they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That device is everything to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let the New UN Government\Ntake custody of this device,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,you can still use it freely,\Nany time you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just let us take it in case\Nsomething should happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit tryin' to throw your authority around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:34.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home! Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:15.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, I think you should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, men! There's a\Nmicloning device in Trad City!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're gonna pounce on them and steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:33.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this will be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:03.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something worrying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:13.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we are attacked by some powerful\Nrioters, like that solider said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:17.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of Zentradi in this city.\NEverything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:19.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the citizens' right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let the military have their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:37.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader, is it really okay for us to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the authority\Nto do anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:44.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! They were about to agree before\Nthat jerk Kaifun butted in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! We're only after the micloning device.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get it, we get the hell out, no delays!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:05.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Hall can accommodate\N3,000 people, including Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you expecting a full house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:13.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Minmay, I'll see to it that\Nit's standing room only!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire city will be behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me show you the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Look a little\Nmore cheerful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disappointing the mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:41.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The rioters know that the micloning\Ndevice is in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they'll attack here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're still thinking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't work yourself up over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful stage. The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we're getting some\Npretty bad news, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly not something to chat\Nabout over a glass of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have discovered the link between\Nus giants and the Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:58.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We giants are a race created for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that the Protoculture made us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.84,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Exsedol, allow me to tell the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It began over 500,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:24.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, a race known as the Protoculture had created one of the most brilliant\Ncivilizations in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point, they split\Ninto two main factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:35.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Protoculture used\Ngenetic engineering to synthesize a race of giants for use in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These were the giants of the Zentradi Forces\Nand the Supervision Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:45.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning, they were\Ndenied any sort of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bodies were large and they were powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:52.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they also had culture, there was a risk that\Nthe Protoculture would be overthrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:59.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, these cultureless giants spent\Nlong ages knowing only battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:07.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Until finally, the frail Protoculture was\Ndestroyed by the very giants
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,they themselves had created.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the communications center!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them contact the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've been in battle.\NIt sure gets the blood pumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The micloning machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:21.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we spent the next 500,000 years\Ndoing nothing but fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:25.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that the Earth people\Naren't the Protoculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not exactly the same, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do we have nearly the\Nsame genes and blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Genetic engineering can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:41.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that the Protoculture's genetic engineering\Nsomehow affected your Earth-born ancestors as well, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not saying that we were\Ncreated too, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:49.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I don't think we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to believe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:55.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the creations of the Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the puppets of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The puppets of the devil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:25.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Only knowing fighting...\NI feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All we ever do is fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible woman, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Trad City's been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the micloning device was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it happened about ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their comm system was down for a while\Nso we just now got word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we send a security detail, hopefully\Nthey'll get there in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:15.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that no matter what we do, we will\Nforever be a race that revels in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:19.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, some of you have already\Nfound another way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, haven't you rejected war yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is still an empty reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:39.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how advanced a culture\Nbecomes, war will always exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the same fate as the people\Nof the Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:49.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot be free of war either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so pessimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:06.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should've just taken it by force,\Nwhether the citizens liked it not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:32.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't I say that Hikaru was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why couldn't I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:21.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'll become so powerful that\NI'll beat all these humans to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:32.93,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I quietly stole away from your empty room
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:39.91,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,To a train station, with no destination
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:35.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:37.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:46.56,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I finally understood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:56.73,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tenderness is the reverse of your weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:51.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:02.53,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've changed too much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:08.25,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:13.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Created for battle, we are the\Npuppets of the devil,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:15.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Satan's dolls."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.00,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,106)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.00,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,454)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:42.76,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin has successfully seized the\Nmicloning device, and escalates his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:49.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,He takes Minmay and Kaifun hostage and demands that\Nthe New UN Forces give him a warship in return for their release.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:54.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan is made to rescue the hostages and\NHikaru has a central role to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:58.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:01.25,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"BROKEN HEART"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:24:02.01,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(114,148)}BROKEN HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:23.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.26,0:24:29.63,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.92,0:24:36.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.52,0:24:44.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:50.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:56.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.90,0:25:04.14,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.45,0:25:15.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
